tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE performance_data ( 
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(255), 
    execution_time FLOAT, 
    accuracy FLOAT, 
    memory_usage DECIMAL(10,2), 
    timestamp TIMESTAMP 
);

CREATE TABLE performance_data
(
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    performance_metric FLOAT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE trend_analysis
(
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    analysis_id INT,
    algorithm_id INT,
    trend_data JSON
);

CREATE TABLE PerformanceData (
    algorithm_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    performance_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE AlgorithmDetails (
    algorithm_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(50),
    author VARCHAR(50),
    description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE TrendAnalysis (
    trend_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    trend_data JSON
)

CREATE TABLE Predictions (
    prediction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_id INT,
    prediction_result VARCHAR(100),
    prediction_accuracy FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE algorithm_metadata (
    algorithm_id INT NOT NULL,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    algorithm_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    created_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);
